2. Delete old `github-actions` token, create new one with **No expiry**
3. Run: `gh secret set RAILWAY_TOKEN --repo alexsiri7/reli` and paste the new token
4. Re-run the failed pipeline: `gh run rerun 25019840901 --repo alexsiri7/reli --failed`

